thread.title: Philip Milnor
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Philip Milnor

author: Philip Milnor
title: Philip Milnor
text: We recently completed a 10 day one way rental from Auckland to Wellington. I want to especially thank the Auckland Office at the airport where we picked up the car. The staff were extremely helpful in trying to help us find a hotel room in the Auckland area as everything was booked. The car ran great and turning the car in was quick and easy in Wellington.
